that.

12:40.493 --> 12:44.597 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But we need it all, we need the
renewable,
we need the non-renewable, we
need the nuclear,

12:44.631 --> 12:48.234 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
we need it all, coal, oil, gas,
