And we're going to use it all to
power our
economy, as well as the country.

12:52.605 --> 12:54.907 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: One final thing,
Senator.

12:54.941 --> 13:00.146 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
