13:14.060 --> 13:15.762 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

13:15.795 --> 13:18.264 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN BARRASSO: Well, I think the
impact in
terms of the optimism that
result of what

13:18.297 --> 13:22.201 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
