expensive, time-consuming,
burdensome.

13:27.240 --> 13:33.146 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And to know that that relief is
coming and
those very expensive regulations
have been

13:33.179 --> 13:37.250 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
