really a good
thing, and people are going to
feel that.

13:37.283 --> 13:43.523 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
When you take a look at what's
happened with
this decision today, it's this
giant step

13:43.556 --> 13:46.726 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
