try to get
back into balance.

13:46.759 --> 13:48.494 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
We all want a clean environment.

13:48.528 --> 13:52.632 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We want to make energy as clean
as we can
as fast as we can in ways that
don't raise

13:52.665 --> 13:54.901 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
