freedom and

14:02.975 --> 14:04.444 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
opportunity.

14:04.477 --> 14:07.847 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Senator John
Barrasso of Wyoming,
