14:07.880 --> 14:08.848 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

14:08.881 --> 14:09.849 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
JOHN BARRASSO: Thanks, Judy.

14:09.882 --> 14:11.684 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
Thanks for having me.

