14:36.943 --> 14:42.582 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But there's a lot of time in
between here
and actually undoing the legacy
of President

14:42.615 --> 14:44.383 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
Obama on this.

14:44.417 --> 14:47.386 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And I want people to understand
that reality,
in terms of where we're going,
it's going

14:47.420 --> 14:51.958 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
to be a difficult slog for this
administration
to undo the great work that we
did the prior

14:51.991 --> 14:53.826 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
