been struggling
for awhile.

16:39.332 --> 16:42.535 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
The simple fact is that it's not
competitive
now.

16:42.568 --> 16:45.404 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
That's why it's not successful
in the market.

16:45.438 --> 16:49.008 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
That's why you see companies,
mining companies
going out of business.

16:49.041 --> 16:54.247 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, it's time to get real with
those people
