18:14.293 --> 18:16.896 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
That's where U.S. strengths
should be.

18:16.929 --> 18:18.831 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
That's where we should be
investing and innovating.

