energy demand.

19:22.028 --> 19:28.401 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We also knew that inexpensive
natural gas
was continuing to compete
against coal, and

19:28.434 --> 19:29.668 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
