again, as a symbolic gesture.

19:58.330 --> 20:01.567 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And what you need to look at is,
where are
utilities spending their money?

20:01.600 --> 20:04.270 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
What is fiscally responsible
now?

20:04.303 --> 20:05.571 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
What's available to them?

20:05.604 --> 20:07.339 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
What are they already doing?

